<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tired-adj">tired <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'taɪəd/    美 /'taɪərd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>疲劳的；累的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a tired child 
疲劳的孩子</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was <strong>too tired to</strong> argue.
他太疲惫了，吵不动了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>厌烦的；厌倦的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was <strong>tired of</strong> the urban life and hoped to move to the country, expecting a change in his current life style. 
他厌倦了城市生活，希望迁居乡村，改变目前的生活方式。</p></div></div>